data.description: This lakeview home offers the perfect blend of comfort, and natural beauty. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this property boasts a master bedroom on the main floor and views of a tranquil lake right in your backyard. The main level offers convenience and privacy with a master suite to revel in the luxury of easy access and seamless integration with the rest of the living space. Indulge in the serenity and beauty of nature with sweeping views of the shimmering lake from several advantage points throughout the home. Whether you're enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings, the tranquil waters provide a picturesque backdrop for every occasion. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a master-on-main home with captivating lake views. Schedule your private showing today and discover the epitome of luxury living!
